'''EarthBrowser''' is a virtual globe software developed by Lunar software. It is available online as a flash application or be installed locally as an [[Adobe Integrated Runtime|AIR]] application. It focuses mainly on visualising geophysical information such as weather, earthquakes, etc.
It shows the earth as satellite images.

