'''Güneyçartar''' (also, '''Gioune-Tchartar''', '''Gyune-Chertaz''', and '''Gyuneychartar''' {{lang-hy|Ղոլզէ Ճարտար}}) is a village ''[[de jure]]'' in the [[Khojavend Rayon]] of [[Azerbaijan]], ''[[de facto]]'' in the [[Martuni Rayon]] of the [[Republic of Artsakh]].

