This is a list of [[freshwater ecoregion]]s as compiled by the [[World Wildlife Fund]] (WWF). The terrestrial scheme divides the Earth's land surface into 8 terrestrial [[ecozone]]s, containing 426 smaller ecoregions. Each ecoregion is classified into one of 12 major habitat types, or [[biome]]s.

