'''Oerlemans''' is a [[Dutch language|Dutch]] [[toponymic surname]] indicating an origin in the town of [[Oerle]], [[North Brabant]].<ref>[http://www.cbgfamilienamen.nl/nfb/detail_naam.php?gba_lcnaam=oerlemans&gba_naam=Oerlemans&nfd_naam=Oerlemans&operator=eq&taal= Oerlemans] at the Database of Surnames in The Netherlands</ref> Notable Dutch people with the surname include:
* [[Daniëlle Overgaag|Daniëlle Oerlemans-Overgaag]] (born 1973), road cyclist, wife of Reinout * [[Hans Oerlemans]] (born 1950), climatologist and glaciologist * [[Jeroen Oerlemans]] (1970-2016), photojournalist * [[Marcel Oerlemans]] (born 1969), football striker * [[Natasja Oerlemans]] (born 1969), Party for the Animals politician * [[Reinout Oerlemans]] (born 1971), actor, director, producer and presenter, husband of Daniëlle
